channel.title: Obviously I have lag
channel.description:
Hello
I made my server open a couple of weeks ago. Ever since it's been open I've had people complaining about lag problems. I had somebody help me before and he got me a new antilag. That helped a good amount of people who have logged into my server, but it hasn't comletely solved the problem. I know it can't be my computer as it isn't slow while running my server at all. So could somebody post some ideas as to how I could solve this problem?
